      "type": "int",
      "defaultValue": "0",
      "help": "When set to 1, USoundWaves we will always attempt to synchronously load a chunk after a USoundWave request has finished. 0: Don't try to block after a SoundWave has completed loading a chunk, 1: Block after a USoundWave's chunk request has completed.",
