      "kind": "variable",
      "type": "int",
      "defaultValue": "3",
      "help": "This can be set to define the default behavior when a USoundWave is loaded. 1: Retain audio data on load, 2: prime audio data on load, 3: load on demand (No audio data is loaded until a USoundWave is played or primed).",
