      "name": "au.streamcaching.DebugView",
      "kind": "variable",
      "type": "int",
      "defaultValue": "2",
      "help": "Enables the comparison of FObjectKeys when comparing Stream Cache Chunk Keys. Without this FName collisions could occur if 2 SoundWaves have the same name. 0: Legacy, 1: Default, 2: Averaged View, 3: High Detail View",
