      "kind": "variable",
      "type": "int",
      "defaultValue": "0",
      "help": "Threshold to avoid imprecision issues on certain GPUs when detecting when a heightmap height changes, i.e. only a height difference > than this threshold (N over 16-bits uint height) will be detected as a change.",
