      "defaultValue": "1",
      "help": "Defines if time is included in each line in the log file and in what form. Layout: [time][frame mod 1000] 0 = Do not display log timestamps 1 = Log time stamps in UTC and frame time (default) e.g. [2015.11.25-21.28.50:803][376] 2 = Log timestamps in seconds elapsed since GStartTime e.g. [0130.29][420] 3 = Log timestamps in local time and frame time e.g. [2017.08.04-17.59.50:803][420] 4 = Log timestamps with the engine's timecode and frame time e.g. [17:59:50:18][420]",
      "category": "Log",
      "availability": {
