      "kind": "variable",
      "type": "int",
      "defaultValue": "0",
      "help": "Time in milliseconds to limit client incoming bunch processing to. If 0, no limit. As long as we're below the limit, will start processing another bunch. A single bunch that takes a while to process can overshoot the limit. After the limit is hit, remaining bunches in a packet are queued, and the IpNetDriver will not process any more packets in the current frame.",
