      "name": "np2.PredictiveInterpolation.ErrorAccAngVelMaxLimit",
      "kind": "variable",
      "type": "float",
      "defaultValue": "1.5",
      "help": "If target angular velocity (in degrees) is below this limit we check for desync to trigger softsnap and accumulate time to build up to a hardsnap.",
