      "kind": "variable",
      "type": "int",
      "defaultValue": "5",
      "help": "If we don't occlusion test a primitive for this many frames, then we expand the BBox when we do occlusion test it for a few frames. See also r.ExpandNewlyOcclusionTestedBBoxesAmount, r.FramesToExpandNewlyOcclusionTestedBBoxes",
