      "kind": "variable",
      "type": "int",
      "defaultValue": "0",
      "help": "Whether to use stencil tests in the prepass, and depth-equal tests in the base pass to implement LOD dithering. If disabled, LOD dithering will be done through clip() instructions in the prepass and base pass, which disables EarlyZ. Forces a full prepass when enabled.",
