      "defaultValue": "1",
      "help": "Whether the default values for AutoExposure should support an extended range of scene luminance. This also change the PostProcessSettings.Exposure.MinBrightness, MaxBrightness, HistogramLogMin and HisogramLogMax to be expressed in EV100 values instead of in Luminance and Log2 Luminance. 0: Legacy range (UE4 default) 1: Extended range (UE5 default)",
