      "kind": "variable",
      "type": "int",
      "defaultValue": "0",
      "help": "Throttle the primary screen percentage allowed by the heuristic to this max value when enabled. This has no effect on preallocated video memory. This is for instance useful when the video game wants to trottle power consumption when inactive without resizing internal renderer's render targets (which can result in popping)",
