      "defaultValue": "1",
      "help": "Mobile default AntiAliasingMethod 0: off (no anti-aliasing) 1: FXAA (default, faster than TemporalAA but much more shimmering for non static cases) 2: TemporalAA(it will fallback to FXAA if SupportsGen4TAA is disabled) 3: MSAA",
