      "defaultValue": "-1",
      "help": "Enable denoising of the path traced output (if a denoiser plugin is active) (default = -1 (driven by postprocesing volume)) -1: inherit from PostProcessVolume 0: disable denoiser 1: enable denoiser (if a denoiser plugin is active)",
