      "name": "r.PathTracing.Override.Depth",
      "kind": "variable",
      "type": "int",
      "defaultValue": "1",
      "help": "Override the scene depth z by the path tracing depth z0: off 1: On (Default, translucent materials have better DOF with the post-process DOF.)",
