      "kind": "variable",
      "type": "int",
      "defaultValue": "1",
      "help": "Attempts to re-use skylight data between frames. (default = 1 (enabled)) When set to 0, the skylight texture and importance samping data will be regenerated every frame. This is mainly intended as a benchmarking and debugging aid",
