      "name": "r.PathTracing.TemporalDenoiser.DeltaE",
      "kind": "variable",
      "type": "int",
      "defaultValue": "5",
      "help": "Cut off the history weight to zero at CIE DeltaE for low frequency. 1.0 :the just noticeable difference (JND), 2.0 :perceptible for close look 10.0:Perceptible at a glance This works as an alternative control instead of kappa. 2 as default.",
