      "name": "r.RayTracing.Geometry.Cable.WPO",
      "kind": "variable",
      "type": "int",
      "defaultValue": "1",
      "help": "World position offset evaluation for cable meshes with EvaluateWPO enabled in ray tracing effects. 0: Cable meshes with world position offset visible in ray tracing, WPO evaluation disabled. 1: Cable meshes with world position offset visible in ray tracing, WPO evaluation enabled (default).",
