      "name": "r.RDG.Breakpoint",
      "kind": "variable",
      "type": "int",
      "defaultValue": "0",
      "help": "Breakpoint in debugger when certain conditions are met. 0: off (default); 1: On an RDG warning; 2: When a graph / pass matching the debug filters compiles; 3: When a graph / pass matching the debug filters executes; 4: When a graph / pass / resource matching the debug filters is created or destroyed;",
      "category": "Rendering",
      "availability": {
        "engineVersions": [
          "5.4"
        ]
      },
