      "kind": "variable",
      "type": "int",
      "defaultValue": "0",
      "help": "Extends the resource lifetimes of resources (or a specific resource filter specified by r.RDG.Debug.ResourceFilter) so that they cannot overlap memory with any other resource within the graph. Useful to debug if transient aliasing is causing issues. 0: disabled (default); 1: enabled;",
