      "type": "int",
      "defaultValue": "0",
      "help": "Enables flushing the GPU after every pass. Disables async compute (r.RDG.AsyncCompute=0) and parallel execute (r.RDG.ParallelExecute=0) when set. 0: disabled (default); 1: enabled.",
