      "defaultValue": "0",
      "help": "Whether to bypass the rhi command list and send the rhi commands immediately. 0: Disable (required for the multithreaded renderer) 1: Enable (convenient for debugging low level graphics API calls, can suppress artifacts from multithreaded renderer code)",
