      "defaultValue": "2",
      "help": "This option enables recomputing the vertex tangents on the GPU. Can be changed at runtime, requires both r.SkinCache.CompileShaders=1, r.SkinCache.Mode=1 and r.SkinCache.Allow=1 0: off 1: on, forces all skinned object to Recompute Tangents 2: on, only recompute tangents on skinned objects who ticked the Recompute Tangents checkbox(default)",
