      "name": "r.SparseVolumeTexture.Streaming.ForceEstimateFrameRate",
      "kind": "variable",
      "type": "int",
      "defaultValue": "0",
      "help": "Forces the streaming system to always estimate the SVT playback frame rate instead of using the explicit frame rate that is passed in with the streaming requests. Intended for debugging.",
