      "kind": "variable",
      "type": "int",
      "defaultValue": "5",
      "help": "Number of SVT streaming system updates to wait until unused streaming instances are cleaned up. A streaming instance is an internal book keeping object to track playback of a SVT asset in a given context. Default: 5",
