      "defaultValue": "0",
      "help": "Basis of the translucency's screen percentage (Experimental). 0: Uses the primary view's resolution (notably scaling with r.ScreenPercentage and r.DynamicRes.*) 1: Uses the secondary view's resolution (temporal upscale's output resolution)",
