      "defaultValue": "0",
      "help": "Render translucent meshes in separate buffer from the scene color. This prevent those meshes from self refracting and leaking scnee color behind over edges when it should be affect by colored transmittance. Forced disabled when r.SeparateTranslucency is 0.",
